{% block bodyContent %}
<p>This page explains how to write NHS App messages, text messages, emails and letters for patients and the public. It gives practical advice on structure, tone and wording so your message is easy to understand and act upon.</p>

<h2 id="who-is-this-guidance-for">Who this guidance is for</h2>

<p>This guidance is for anyone who writes or edits patient messages, including:</p>
<ul>
  <li>content designers</li>
  <li>communications teams</li>
  <li>administrations staff </li>
</ul>
{% from "inset-text/macro.njk" import insetText %}

{% set insetTextHtml %}
